title: Ep254 Renaissance Festival Crimes
description:
This week, the gals bust out their best bustiers to talk about a favorite festival pastime. Topics include the historical accuracy of turkey legs, a kinky campground, and a very unfortunate genetic trait. Fill your goblet with High Noon, pack some extra wet wipes, and tune in for Renaissance Festival Crimes.                                                                                     

For a full list of show sponsors, visit https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
